This is it!

53
00:03:33,070 --> 00:03:35,480
Sabaody Archipelago!

54
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:37,650
At the seemingly enjoyable archipelago,

55
00:03:37,650 --> 00:03:40,820
Luffy and company searched
for a coating craftsman...

56
00:03:42,150 --> 00:03:44,910
...but they encountered world
nobles known as Celestial Dragons

57
00:03:44,910 --> 00:03:47,580
and were witness to their
domineering behavior.

58
00:03:47,940 --> 00:03:48,830
Damn it!

59
00:03:48,830 --> 00:03:51,210
If only... If only it wasn't for this!

60
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:55,910
Honestly, now!

61
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:57,920
You're terrible at taking care of them!

62
00:03:58,190 --> 00:03:59,380
You make me sick.

63
00:04:01,300 --> 00:04:01,980
She's...!

64
00:04:01,980 --> 00:04:03,050
Stop! Please!

65
